64:     // When used for a
65:     // :ref:`on_header_present <envoy_v3_api_field_extensions.filters.http.header_to_metadata.v3.Config.Rule.on_header_present>`
66:     // case, if value is non-empty it'll be used instead of the header value. If both are empty, no metadata is added.
